en_117654_0	Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has instructed the relevant officials to implement a programme of providing speedy relief to persons displaced by floods and landslides.
en_117654_1	While seven deaths due to landslides at ‘Lilly’s Land’ Estate in Vedamulla in the Nuwara-Eliya district was reported, 19 families were displaced.
en_117654_2	The Prime Minister’s office said that the Government had released Rs4 million for the displaced persons to construct temporary residences.
en_117654_3	Steps have also been taken to relocate 19 families residing in disaster-prone sites.
